            <span class="text-green-600 font-black flex-shrink-0">‚úì</span>
            <span>Ran 20 tests per builder (10 desktop, 10 mobile), averaged results</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-green-600 font-black flex-shrink-0">‚úì</span>
