        <div class="bg-white p-6 mt-6 border-l-4 border-gray-600">
          <p class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">Why 20 tests per builder?</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Single test = random variance. Server load, network congestion, CDN caching‚Äîtoo many variables. 20 tests = statistical significance. Outliers removed = clean data. Average = truth.</p>
        </div>
